oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Ken Speck Job No. 38187
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm); Miller, Roger, 1936-1992;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 2714) for an order placed by Ken Speck for 500 two color jumbos for a performance by Roger Miller on May 15. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
